  "code": "---\ntitle: ReciMe ER Diagram\n---\nerDiagram\n    Users ||..o| Chefs :ISA\n    Users ||..o{ Recipes :posts\n    Users ||..o{ Reviews :writes\n    Users ||..o{ Reviews :likes\n    Users ||..o{ Favorites :has\n    Users ||..o{ Ratings : gives\n    Recipes ||..o| Favorites :ISA\n    Recipes ||..o{ Reviews :has\n    Recipes ||..o{ Ratings :has\n    Recipes||..o{ Categories :has\n    Reviews ||..o| MarkedReviews :ISA\n    Users ||..o{ MarkedReviews :marks\n    Chefs ||..o| CertifiedChefs :ISA   \n",
  "diagram_type": "er size:400..600",
  "collected_at": "2026-02-27T03:40:14.087909",
  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为ReciMe设计一个ER图。核心实体是用户和食谱，用户会发布食谱，这个关系要体现出来。另外用户之间还有层级关系——普通用户可以升级为厨师。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Users",
        "Recipes",
        "Chefs",
        "posts",
        "ISA"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。Users到Chefs用ISA继承关系，一个用户最多只能是一个厨师。那用户和食谱的发布关系是\"posts\"，一对多对吗？一个用户可以发多篇食谱。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Users",
        "Chefs",
        "Recipes",
        "posts"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。另外用户还会写评论，这个评论实体需要包含用户点赞的功能——用户可以给自己喜欢的评论点like。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Users",
        "Reviews",
        "writes",
        "likes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我加上Reviews实体，Users通过writes和likes两个关系连接过去。那食谱这边呢？评论应该是挂在食谱下面的吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reviews",
        "Users",
        "Recipes",
        "writes",
        "likes",
        "has"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，Recipes要有has关系指向Reviews。另外还需要评分和收藏功能——用户可以给食谱打分，也可以收藏食谱。这里有个细节：收藏本质上是一种特殊的食谱聚合，我考虑让Favorites继承自Recipes。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Recipes",
        "Reviews",
        "Ratings",
        "Favorites",
        "has",
        "gives",
        "ISA"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Favorites继承Recipes？这是说收藏夹里的条目本身就是一种食谱的视图？那用户和Favorites的关系是has，一对多。评分Ratings也是用户gives给Recipes的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Favorites",
        "Recipes",
        "Users",
        "Ratings",
        "has",
        "gives",
        "ISA"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对。还有分类Categories，食谱可以属于多个分类。另外评论需要标记功能——有些优质评论会被标记为MarkedReviews，这是评论的子类，由用户来marks。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Categories",
        "Recipes",
        "MarkedReviews",
        "Reviews",
        "marks",
        "ISA"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了，Recipes和Categories是多对多的has关系。MarkedReviews继承Reviews，Users通过marks关联过去。最后厨师这边，CertifiedChefs应该是Chefs的进一步特化吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Categories",
        "MarkedReviews",
        "Reviews",
        "Users",
        "CertifiedChefs",
        "Chefs",
        "has",
        "marks",
        "ISA"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，CertifiedChefs是认证厨师，继承自Chefs。整个结构应该完整了，你再检查一下关系基数有没有问题。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CertifiedChefs",
        "Chefs",
        "ISA"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "我发现刚才Favorites的ISA方向画反了，应该是Recipes指向Favorites。还有Users到MarkedReviews的marks关系，我确认一下是用户标记评论，不是评论标记用户，已经修正。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Favorites",
